text: Alhaz Jamirun Noor High School is a public secondary school in Sunamganj Sadar Upazila, Sunamganj District, Bangladesh. It was established in 1990 by Alhaz Abdur noor Talukder. It is situated in Janigoan. The school consists of three main buildings. There is one playground inside the school compound. ==References== ==External links== * Bangla Medium School * Secondary Schools In Bangladesh Category:High schools in Bangladesh
